hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Could I take your name and number, please? can you drink whilst on accutane As I leave, Chloe and Amy are sitting at the kitchen table, playing with their phones and flicking through a copy of Hello!. Henry appears through the open door with his rescue dog, Sandy, to collect some jeans Alex has altered for him. ‘Perhaps I needed to feel loved and wanted,’ Alex says, plopping down on a kitchen chair occupied by a highly vocal and slightly delinquent-looking cat. ‘I certainly wanted and loved them all. It hasn’t always been easy, but I feel I’ve had a lovely life and it’s been hugely enriched by these wonderful young people who have crossed my path.’
